  "identifier": "HB 276",
  "title": "AN ACT relating to keeping chickens on residential property.",
  "abstract": "Create a new section of KRS Chapter 65 to define \"backyard chicken\"; allow a person to keep 6 or fewer backyard chickens on residential property in cities and certain other local governments; establish requirements and restrictions on local regulatory authority.",
